ay</strong>\" influences the work we do and the way we look after our customers, and they\'ll tell you that even in his early 80\'s, Jim still plays a very active and valuable part in our company.</p>\r\n<p>Masterton Homes has now been part of the NSW home building community for half a century. Jim\'s legacy will live on for decades to come, through generations of the Masterton family now actively involved in the business - and through the values he instilled in all of us over the years.</p>\r\n<p>There will always be \"Jim\'s Way\", and we\'ll always respect and honour the lessons Jim taught us.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>','The Masterton Story','','publish','open','open','','the-masterton-story','','','2015-04-22 11:34:02','2015-04-22 11:34:02','',0,'http://realestate.taichinh-24h.com/?page_id=302',0,'page','',0),(303,1,'2015-04-09 17:32:54','2015-04-09 17:32:54','','The Masterton Story','','inherit','open','open','','302-revision-v1','','','2015-04-09 17:32:54','2015-04-09 17:32:54','',302,'http://realestate.taichinh-24h.com/302-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(304,1,'2015-04-09 17:33:17','2015-04-09 17:33:17','<div id=\"dnn_ctr440_HtmlModule_lblContent\" class=\"Normal\">From <strong>Tea Gardens </strong>to <strong>Bermagui</strong> - From <strong>Wollongong</strong> to <strong>Narooma</strong> and throughout<strong> Sydney</strong>, more home buyers are getting a whole lot more when they choose their new Masterton home. Masterton are one of the pre-eminent builders in NSW. Our organisation is set up to build almost anywhere and everywhere in the State.\r\n<p>Find your nearest <a href=\"http://masterton.com.au/LinkClick.aspx?link=84&amp;tabid=95&amp;mid=440\">Masterton Display Location</a>.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"Normal\">\r\n<p><a href=\"http://realestate.taichinh-24h.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Where-we-build-2014.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-364 size-full\" src=\"http://r