INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (345,1,'2015-04-09 17:58:39','2015-04-09 17:58:39','There aren\'t too many people in NSW that haven\'t heard of Jim Masterton. Truthfully, Jim\'s also pretty well known around the other states of Australia too, which isn\'t surprising when you\'ve spent over fifty years of your life in the same industry, and can boast to have built 50,000 new homes for Australian families over that time.\r\n\r\nAsk anyone at Masterton how \"Jim\'s Way\" influences the work we do and the way we look after our customers, and they\'ll tell you that even in his early 80\'s, Jim still plays a very active and valuable part in our company.\r\n\r\nMasterton Homes has now been part of the NSW home building community for half a century. Jim\'s legacy will live on for decades to come, through generations of the Masterton family now actively involved in the business - and through the values he instilled in all of us over the years.\r\n\r\nThere will always be \"Jim\'s Way\", and we\'ll always respect and honour the lessons Jim taught us.','Building quality homes since 1962','','publish','closed','closed','','building-quality-homes-since-1962','','','2015-04-09 17:58:39','2015-04-09 17:58:39','',0,'http://realestate.taichinh-24h.com/?post_type=homeland&#038;p=345',0,'homeland','',0),(346,1,'2015-04-09 17:59:19','2015-04-09 17:59:19','Base price includes traditional facade. Alternative facade upgrades available. No applied finishes are included such as render, moroka, bag and paint, stack stone or tiles. These are optional upgrades. Images in this brochure may depict items not supplied by Masterton which include, but are not limited to, landscaping, pathways, driveways, decks, pergolas, fencing, letter boxes, pool, water features and BBQ. Images may depict upgraded items which include, but are not limited to, fireplaces, window furnishings, light fittings, floor coverings, alarm systems, air conditioning, doors and feature tiling. Masterton reserves the right to revise plans, specifications and pricing without notice. All plans and images are subject to copyright protection. Please contact a sales consultant for more information.\r\n\r\nMasterton Homes Pty Ltd ABN 52 002 873 047 BLicence 35558C, Masterton Canberra Pty Ltd ABN 98 142 017 089 BLicence 2010666.','YES INCLUSSIONS Special Offers','','publish','closed','closed','','yes-inclussions-special-offers','','','2015-04-09 17:59:19','2015-04-09 17:59:19','',0,'http://realestate.taichinh-24h.com/?post_type=homeland&#038;p=346',0,'homeland','',0),(348,1,'2015-04-20 04:07:14','2015-04-20 04:07:14','','Home & Land Packages','','publish','open','open','','home-land-packages','','','2015-04-20 04:07:14','2015-04-20 04:07:14','',0,'http://realestate.taichinh-24h.com/?page_id=348',0,'page','',0),(349,1,'2015-04-20 04:07:14','2015-04-20 04:07:14','','Home & Land Packages','','inherit','open','open','','348-revision-v1','','','2015-04-20 04:07:14','2015-04-20 04:07:14','',348,'http://realestate.taichinh-24h.com/348-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(350,1,'2015-04-20 04:07:42','2015-04-20 04:07:42','<p><a href=\"http://realestate.taichinh-24h.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/How-to-buy-banner-950px-wide.jpg\"><img class=\" size-full wp-image-359 aligncenter\" src=\"http://realestate.taichinh-24h.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/How-to-buy-banner-950px-wide.jpg\" alt=\"How to buy banner 950px wide\" width=\"950\" height=\"191\" /></a> </p>\r\n<div id=\"dnn_ctr613_HtmlModule_lblContent\" class=\"Normal\">\r\n<h1>1. Select your New Home and Land Package<img style=\"width: 312px; height: 960px; float: right; margin-right: 30px; margin-left: 5px;\" src=\"http://realestate.taichinh-24h.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Image-strip-02.jpg\" alt=\"House &amp; Land Process\" width=\"312\" height=\"960\" /></h1>\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Talk with our helpful sales team to select the best suited <br /> </span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Home and Land Package to meet your requirements and budget.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h1>2. Tailor your New Masterton Home</h1>\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Make those small changes to suit your needs for your <br /> </span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">new Masterton Home.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h1>3. Secure your New Home and Land Package</h1>\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">All you need is $1,000 as an initial holding fee.<br /> - This takes the Home and Land Package \'Off the Market\'</span></span>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Within <strong>7 days </strong>of paying your initial holding fee:<br /> - We will produce a New Home Proposal for you to review<br /> - This is a document that provides the inclusions and a fixed price<br /> for your new Home and Land Packafge</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Within <strong>9 days</strong> of reviewing your New Home Proposal:<br /> - All you need to pay is an additional $2,500 and we will commence <br /> drawing your plans and other necessary documents arranged<br /> - This is your final opportunity to make any changes</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Within <strong>35 days </strong>from signing and paying you New Home Proposal<br /> - Your plans will be presented to you and your building contract<br /> will be produced<br /> - This is where you sign your building contract and pay the building<br /> contract deposit of 5% of the home price less the $3,500 already paid</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">We will then \'nominate\' you as the purchaser of the lot to the Developer<br /> and you will receive a land contract shortly thereafter.<br /> - You then sign the land contract and pay the developer exchange deposit<br /> amount (up to 10% of the land price) within <strong>14 days</strong> from signing and <br /> paying your build contract </span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">In the time between nomination and the land registering<br /> - You have the exciting time selecting all your colours, fittings etc. <br /> as detailed in your building contract for your new Masterton Home</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">We then wait until the land registers<br /> - This is where you settle the land with the Developer (the land price<br /> less land deposit paid)</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Masterton will then start construction of your new home a short time after,<br /> once the appropriate approvals are received.<br /> </span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div> </div>\r\n<div>Please note:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>If you are not able to meet these time frames, you may lose the opportunity to proceed with the Home and Land Package or the price may increase</li>\r\n<li>The fixed price is based on the Developer provided anticipated land registration date</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Home & Land Process','','publish','open','open','','home-land-process','','','2015-04-22 11:47:26','2015-04-22 11:47:26','',0,'http://realestate.taichinh-24h.com/?page_id=350',0,'page','',0),(351,1,'2015-04-20 04:07:42','2015-04-20 04:07:42','','Home & Land Process','','inherit','open','open','','350-revision-v1','','','2015-04-20 04:07:42','2015-04-20 04:07:42','',350,'http://realestate.taichinh-24h.com/350-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(352,1,'2015-04-20 04:09:13','2015-04-20 04:09:13',' ','','','publish','open','open','','352','','','2015-04-26 16:15:4